<p>
  To start initial teacher training, you’ll need to have a degree or equivalent
  qualification.
</p>

<p>You’ll also need:</p>

<ul>
  <li>English GCSE grade 4 (C) or above</li>
  <li>Maths GCSE grade 4 (C) or above</li>
  <li>Science GCSE grade 4 (C) or above if you want to teach in primary education</li>
</ul>

<p>
  <a href="/guidance/become-a-teacher-in-england#if-you-do-not-have-a-degree">Find out what to do if you do not have a degree</a>.
</p>

